Package com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.configuration

Interface IGApplicationConfiguration.IGTenantInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GApplicationConfiguration.GTenantInfo, GCOMApplicationConfiguration.GCOMTenantInfo
    Enclosing interface:
    IGApplicationConfiguration
    public static interface IGApplicationConfiguration.IGTenantInfo
    Structure describing Tenant which is referred in the server application configuration.
    It reflects detached information from COM AB CfgTenant.
    See Also:
    CfgTenant
